item.title: Colman Domingo - 'Sing Sing' [LIVE]
item.description: In front of an audience of film students at Chapman University, the 'Rustin' Oscar nominee and 'Euphoria' Emmy winner reflects on his decades of work before anyone was paying attention, how close he came to walking away from the profession in 2014 and the career renaissance that he was enjoyed over the past decade.
